A 2010 [[Ofsted]] report said that "This is a satisfactory school. Some areas of its work are good."<ref>Ofsted [http://www.ofsted.gov.uk/oxedu_reports/display/(id)/120824 Filey School], Section 5 inspection published 14 June 2010</ref>
